The red and blue colours represent the most negative potential (electron-rich) and positive potential (electrondeficient) parts of the graphene and rGO-4-PP Nc. Analysis of this result clearly indicate that the ESP distribution of graphene is very uniform for the identical elements, which is significantly different from the situations of rGO-4-PP Nc. In rGO-4-PP Nc,

